msgid "ndarray, optional"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.vecdot:22
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have the "
"broadcasted shape of `x1` and `x2` with the last axis removed. If not "
"provided or None, a freshly-allocated array is used."
msgstr ""

